{"tid":1853474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消息指政府將公布延長公務員留家工作　考慮全港中小學幼稚園再延遲復課","createTime":"2020-01-31T04:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:22:31.000Z","uid":60219,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5bafca5541d5f87b267fda5e8de1303208c3f456","tid":1853474,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"為減低疫情在社區擴散風險，政府在28日宣布，除了提供緊急和必需的公共服務，公務員可毋須到寫字樓辦公，留在家中工作，有關安排原本只至周日（2月2日）為止。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，政府今天將公布公務員留家工作的安排，將延長推行。<br />\n<br />\n至於不少家長關注的停課安排。全港中小學、幼稚園，以及特殊學校原本延遲至2月17日復課，據了解最新評估是有關停課安排會延長。<br />\n<br />\n而武漢肺炎疫情蔓延，世衞將疫情升級，消息指政府有措施進一步減少中港兩地人流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2552934/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%80%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E5%86%8D%E5%BB%B6%E9%81%B2%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2552934%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E7%25A8%259A%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25AA%25B2&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=cd8b8391\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2552934/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E5%BB%